parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates and blinks
the passenger airbag indicator comes on
the airbag system stops working
the cruise control stops working
the airbag light remains on
and the airbag may not deploy in an accident.

symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates and blinks
the passenger airbag indicator comes on
the airbag system stops working
and the airbag may not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard near the airbag can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Cracks appear on the dashboard near the airbag
the airbag deploys without warning
and the airbag light illuminates and blinks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger occupancy sensor can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to the airbag not deploying in an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.

and the airbag system stops working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the floorboards can lead to a safety hazard, as the structural integrity of the vehicle is compromised, and the driver and passengers may be at risk of injury.
symptoms: Visible rust and corrosion on the floorboards
holes in the floorboards
soft or spongy feeling when stepping on the floorboards
carpeting sagging or falling through the floorboards.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission whining and hesitation can lead to a loss of control of the vehicle, increasing the risk of accidents.

hesitation when shifting gears
difficulty accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the hood and door hinges can lead to a safety hazard, as the structural integrity of the vehicle is compromised, and the driver and passengers may be at risk of injury.

difficulty opening and closing the hood and doors.
